                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group" style="position:relative;">
                            <label>Preferred College (Optional)</label>
                            <input type="text" name="preferred_college" id="collegeSearch" placeholder="Type college name to search..." autocomplete="off">
                            <div class="college-dropdown" id="collegeDropdown"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="motivation-text">🎉 Complete now to know your <span>scholarship benefits</span>!</div>
                        <div class="nav-buttons">
                            <button type="button" class="nav-btn prev" id="step4Prev"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Back</button>
                            <button type="button" class="nav-btn next" id="step4Next">Continue <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></button>
                        </div>
